      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Conclusion"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "We have demonstrated that persistent balanced BSTs can achieve the same amortized time complexity as their ephemeral counterparts. Future work includes extending these results to concurrent persistent structures."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Driscoll, J.R. et al. (1989). Making Data Structures Persistent."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "label": "driscoll1989",
      "type": "footnote_def"
    },
    {
      "children": [
